articles.title: Skull of prehistoric 'giant goose' discovered in Australia - BBC.com
articles.description: The fossilised skull of a now extinct flightless bird is a “stunningly rare find”, researchers say.
articles.content:
Genyornis newtoni became extinct some 45,000 years ago
